Spray me for six bucks.

1936
01:55:17.375 --> 01:55:18.541
[chuckles]

1937
01:55:24.416 --> 01:55:25.666
One more.

1938
01:55:25.750 --> 01:55:27.375
Six!

1939
01:55:28.666 --> 01:55:29.791
Sir. sir. sir.

1940
